Class DrinksBrand

  • java.lang.Object
    • sg.edu.nus.iss.vmcs.store.StoreObject
      • sg.edu.nus.iss.vmcs.store.DrinksBrand

  • public class DrinksBrand
extends StoreObject
    This entity object stores the name of the drink brand and its price. There can be as many drink brands as desire, for a particular configuration.
